<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
  body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #222; line-height: 1.7; }
  .letterhead { text-align: center; border-bottom: 3px solid #361963; padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .company-name { font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; color: #361963; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .company-address { font-size: 11px; color: #666; }
  .ref-line { font-size: 11px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .subject { font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 15px; text-decoration: underline; }
  .content p { margin-bottom: 12px; text-align: justify; }
  .signature { margin-top: 60px; }
  .signature-line { border-top: 1px solid #333; width: 200px; margin-top: 50px; }
  table.details { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0; }
  table.details td { padding: 6px 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
  table.details td:first-child { font-weight: bold; width: 40%; background: #f9f9f9; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="letterhead">
    <div class="company-name">{{companyLegalName}}</div>
    <div class="company-address">{{companyAddress}}</div>
    {{#if companyPan}}<div class="company-address">PAN: {{companyPan}}</div>{{/if}}
  </div>

  <div class="ref-line">Date: {{today}}</div>

  <p>Dear <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>

  <div class="subject">OFFER OF EMPLOYMENT</div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>We are pleased to offer you the position of <strong>{{designation}}</strong> in the <strong>{{department}}</strong> department at {{companyLegalName}}. This offer is subject to the terms outlined below.</p>

    <table class="details">
      <tr><td>Position</td><td>{{designation}}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Department</td><td>{{department}}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Annual CTC</td><td>{{formatCurrency annualCTC}}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Date of Joining</td><td>{{formatDate dateOfJoining}}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Location</td><td>{{officeLocation}}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Employment Type</td><td>{{employmentType}}</td></tr>
    </table>

    <p>This offer is contingent upon successful completion of background verification and submission of all required documents on or before your date of joining.</p>

    <p>Please confirm your acceptance by signing and returning a copy of this letter within 7 days of receipt.</p>

    <p>We look forward to welcoming you to the team.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="signature">
    <p>Warm regards,</p>
    <div class="signature-line"></div>
    <p><strong>Authorized Signatory</strong></p>
    <p>{{companyLegalName}}</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
